OL,7,FIf Vladimir Putin ever goes on trial
OL,8,Ffor his savage invasion of Ukraine,
OL,9,Fone brave Russian lawyer says it
OL,10,Fwould be an "honour" to fight his
OL,11,Fcountry's dictator in court. His name
OL,12,Fis Vadim Prokhorov.
OL,14,FThey share initials and a nationality
OL,15,Fbut that's about all the two men have
OL,16,Fin common. Prokhorov has dedicated
OL,17,Fhis legal career to helping Putin's
OL,18,Fopponents, including some who have
OL,19,Fbeen killed for their beliefs.
OL,3,CThe Russian lawyer in exile for
OL,4,Cdefending Putin's biggest critics and
OL,5,Cdreams of prosecuting him
